<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-09-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-09-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="595" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d595">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">394.31/9–1251: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The United States</hi> (<gloss target="#t_GATT1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">GATT</hi></gloss>) <hi rend="italic">Delegation to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                            </seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-09-21">September 21,
                                1951</date>—noon.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <gloss target="#t_Tagg1">Tagg</gloss> 19. Re <gloss target="#t_Embtel1">Embtel</gloss> 1296, repeated Geneva 9. UK, substantial number
                            other dels have agreed support US proposal for severance <gloss target="#t_GATT1">GATT</gloss> relations with Czech. Still talking
                            to Fr and agreement believed very near. For your information Schuman has
                            promised Secy Fr wld reconsider their earlier opposition. Wld appreciate
                            continued <gloss target="#t_Emb1">Emb</gloss> help in obtaining
                            satisfactory instructions to Ital del.</p>
                        <p>Sent Rome 9, rptd info Dept <gloss target="#t_Tagg1">Tagg</gloss> 19.</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>